<p>Amidst the dynamic landscape of Polygon governance, sustaining active participation presents multifaceted challenges requiring innovative solutions to maintain its integrity. </p>



<p>It&#8217;s essential to address these challenges to ensure the continued success of decentralized governance on Polygon.</p>



